  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>For breakfast you'll have a buffet with lots of choices. Breakfast is open from 7 - 11am. Dinner is a la carte and you can enjoy a choice of three courses. The restaurant serves typical Ligurian style food as well as a range of international dishes, so there's something for everyone. Dinner is served from 7 - 9pm</p>]]></cateringDescription>
