  <description><![CDATA[<p>Park Hotel Argento's in the best location for making the most out of Levanto and all that the <a data-udi="umb://document/79a94ac27eda4c2ea223bc0fe7fd99b6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/79a94ac27eda4c2ea223bc0fe7fd99b6}" title="Cinque Terre Area" data-anchor="#">Cinque Terre</a> has to offer.</p>
<h2>Peaceful location, near the beach</h2>
<p>The hotel's far enough from the hustle and bustle of town that you can relax and enjoy some peace and quiet but close enough that you can get out and explore at a moments notice. You'll be within ten minutes of the beach, centre of town and the train station. Hop on a train to a nearby towns like Monterosso and Vernazza and discover all the fantastic walking trails in the Cinque Terre national park. </p>
<h2>Welcoming atmosphere and stylish interiors</h2>
<p>The staff at the hotel are really knowledgeable about Levanto and the Cinque Terre area, they're fantastic people to ask if you want any local tips! The hotels' style is modern with minimalist decor. You'll have everything you need for your ideal Cinque Terre walking holiday and the best part is you can come back to the hotel after a long day exploring the walking trails and treat yourself to a massage (payable locally) or a wind down session in the sauna and steam room.</p>]]></description>
