  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Double Rooms </strong>sleep up to three people. These rooms are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Double Balcony Rooms</strong> sleep up to four people and have a balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Suites </strong>sleep up to four people and have a separate living area.</p>
<p><strong>Double rooms for sole use </strong>are also available, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Air-conditioning</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Shower</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Bathrobe &amp; slippers</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p>Cots are available on request.</p>
<p><strong>Local fees &amp; taxes</strong></p>
<p>A local tourist tax of approx. €3 per person per night is payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Useful Information</strong></p>
<ul>
